article.description: — Sam Alexis had 18 points in Chattanooga's 72-56 win over Southeast Missouri State on Sunday.
article.headline: Chattanooga secures 72-56 win over Southeast Missouri State
article.linkText: Chattanooga secures 72-56 win over Southeast Missouri State
article.story: CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. -- — Sam Alexis had 18 points in Chattanooga's 72-56 win over Southeast Missouri State on Sunday. Alexis contributed nine rebounds for the Mocs (5-1). Honor Huff also scored 18 points and Jan Zidek finished with 16. Adam Larson led the way for the Redhawks (1-5) with 13 points. Rob Martin added 10 points and five assists.
